<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_eb91fc0c-5f45-45ee-a5dd-296947a83366" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="VIC"><sptc>D2D24</sptc><title id="_bf258ea1-3d17-46ff-8945-7a8db1fdfc5a">Doorways to a children’s room</title><subclause id="_4ee48f74-ffd0-494f-a3a8-7bd556435458" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_2d4ba7ff-7f35-4c47-bffc-7888e008e789">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>In an <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/1251_2.4.0.xml#_9ff8fad7-8992-4708-be17-784d962a0530" id="_29700f09-cf52-4f0f-bfa2-131c9f68c6a0" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">early childhood centre</xref>, a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/10621_0.4.0.xml#_1856d29f-7649-45dd-8439-d52fd65d03a4" id="_4eba25c8-1ec5-40fd-a9f7-39b3ce6fb8fa" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">children’s room</xref> must—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_1523cb8d-ae5d-4686-8d4b-ddf4432e336a">have a doorway providing direct access to or form—<ol><li>an outdoor play area; or</li><li>a passage leading to an outdoor area, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/1385_0.4.0.xml#_b4a20ca6-0197-4381-9e50-85c757fa574f" id="_cf3bad38-d791-48af-b4fb-213de98dd092" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">open space</xref> or other safe egress point; or</li><li>a fire-isolated <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/1263_2.3.0.xml#_9712f630-8cf7-401b-b1cc-ae0be4485915" id="_152ee9f5-858f-403a-ba87-a4ed83d8f417" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">exit</xref>; and</li></ol></li><li id="_780e3601-6e93-4556-9161-0249f6c040b1">where the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/10621_0.4.0.xml#_1856d29f-7649-45dd-8439-d52fd65d03a4" id="_88fd452b-7cca-4c2b-8a43-e1c3af0774e2" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">children’s room</xref> accommodates more than 21 children, at least two doorways complying with (a) that are separated as far as practicable.</li></ol></subclause></clause>